  <div id="sg-banner-messages" class="sg-section">
    <div class="sg-h2">Banner messages</div>
    <div class="sg-callout sg-callout-info">
      <div class="sg-callout-title">JS Options</div>
      <code><pre>
{
  project: 'projectJsName',
  hideJs: true, // if hideJs == true, hideClass is note needed
  hideClass: 'hide-banner', // class to animate the hide if hideJs = false
  hiddenClass: 'as--hidden', // class to remove when banner is hidden by default
  caping: 0,
  container: '.c-banner-messages',
  availableDuration: 13,
}
      </pre>
      </code>
      <div class="sg-callout-title">
        <br>HTML Options
      </div>
      <code><pre>
{
  banner: 'bannerName',
  hideJs: true,
  hideClass: 'hide-banner',
  hiddenClass: 'as--hidden',
  caping: 3,
  availableDuration: 13,
}
        </pre>
      </code>

    </div>
    <div class="sg-callout sg-callout-info">
      <div class="sg-callout-title">Usage</div>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="col-6_mq3-12">
          <p><strong>If you click on the consent button <code>.js-banner-btn-accept</code> :</strong><br> - the banner close<br> - the cookie `projectJsName``bannerName` is create<br> - the the banner won't display again for 13 month
            duration.<br> <br> <strong>If you click on the close button <code>.js-banner-btn-close</code> :</strong><br> - the banner close<br> - the sessionStorage item `projectJsName``bannerName` is create<br> - the banner won't display
            until you close your session. </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6_mq3-12">
          <p>
            <strong>If you don't click on these two button and don't set <code>caping</code> option :</strong><br> - the banner will still display if you reload or change page.<br> <br> <strong>If you don't click on these two button and set
              <code>caping</code> option (n > 0) :</strong><br> - the banner will display <strong>n</strong> times if you reload or change page.<br> - <strong>THEN</strong>, the banner won't display any more until you close your session.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sg-callout sg-callout-warning">
      <p>The button <code>.sg-banner-messages-reset</code> is only used in the styleguide.<br> Never use it in your website. </p>
    </div>
