      <p>The <code>img</code> is crop with the css property object-fit</p><br>
      <div class="sg-callout-title">Options</div>
      <ul>
        <li><code>[data-pict="top"]</code> (force align top)</li>
        <li><code>[data-pict="bottom"]</code> (force align bottom)</li>
        <li><code>[data-pict="left"]</code> (force align left)</li>
        <li><code>[data-pict="right"]</code> (force align right)</li>
        <li><code>[data-pict="bg-contain"]</code> (force bg size contain)</li>
        <li><code>[data-pict="default"]</code> (restore image default size)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
